## 建立训练集和测试集
## train_X(训练集数据集X)，train_Y(训练集目标值Y);
## test_X(测试集数据集X)，test_Y(测试集目标值Y);
## 裁剪后的图像尺寸为IMG_HEIGHT，IMG_WIDTH
train_X=[];train_Y=[]
test_X=[];test_Y=[]
IMG_HEIGHT=IMG_WIDTH=64
sys.stdout.flush()
train_folders=next(os.walk(train_dir))[1]
test_folders=next(os.walk(test_dir))[1]
print('开始读训练集图像文件...')
for folder in train_folders:
    PATH=os.path.join(train_dir,folder)
    train_imgs=os.listdir(PATH)
    print('读文件夹'+folder)
    for n, id_ in tqdm(enumerate(train_imgs), total=len(train_imgs)):
        train_img_path=os.path.join(PATH,id_)
        I=img.imread(train_img_path)
        cropped_img= resize(I, (IMG_HEIGHT, IMG_WIDTH), mode='constant', preserve_range=True)
        train_X.append(cropped_img)
        
        train_Y.append(folder)
    print('文件夹'+folder+'读完成!\n')
print('训练集图像文件读完成!!!\n')

print('开始读测试集图像文件...')
for folder in test_folders:
    PATH=os.path.join(test_dir,folder)
    test_imgs=os.listdir(PATH)
    for id_ in test_imgs:
        test_img_path=os.path.join(PATH,id_)
        I=img.imread(test_img_path)
        cropped_img= resize(I, (IMG_HEIGHT, IMG_WIDTH), mode='constant', preserve_range=True)
        test_X.append(cropped_img)
        
        test_Y.append(folder)
print('测试集图像文件读完成!!!')

def ret_label(one_hot_list):
    '''给定一个独热编码后的列表，返回map_dic的键，如输入[1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]，返回building'''
    for _ in map_dic.items():
        if one_hot_list in _:
            return (_[0])

def show(img,label):
    '''给定numpy数组类型的图像，和标签label，作可视化'''
    fig=plt.figure(figsize=(12,12))
    for i in range(64):
        plt.subplot(8,8,i+1)
        plt.imshow(img[i].astype(np.uint8))
        plt.title("{0}".format(ret_label(label[i].tolist())))
        plt.axis('off')
    plt.show()

##### 小批量数据生成器
def gen_small_data(inputs,Labels,batch_size):
    i=0
    while True:
        small_data=inputs[i:(batch_size+i)]
        small_label=Labels[i:(batch_size+i)]
        i+=batch_size
        yield small_data,small_label

搭建卷积神经网络¶

In [30]:
import time
epochs=10 #网络训练次数
learning_rate=0.01 #学习率
batch_size=128 #训练块的大小(mini-batch SGD)
batch_num=int(train_X_shuffle.shape[0]/batch_size) #块的数目

filter_width=3 #滤波器的宽度
filter_height=3 #滤波器的高度
depth_in=3 #输入数据通道数
depth_out1=200 #隐含层1的通道数(特征数目)
depth_out2=150#隐含层2的通道数(特征数目)
f_height=64 #输入图像尺寸

######输入
n_classes=6 ##手写字体10个类
x_=tf.placeholder(tf.float32,[batch_size,64,64,3]) #输入数据为100*100的图像，batch_size表示每次的训练样本个数
y_=tf.placeholder(tf.float32,[batch_size,n_classes]) #输出数据为6个类别

######ops:Weights and bias
Weights={"wc1":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([filter_height,filter_width,depth_in,depth_out1])),\
        "wc2":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([filter_height,filter_width,depth_out1,depth_out2])),\
        "wd1":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([int((f_height*f_height/16)*depth_out2),256])),\
         "wd2":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([512,100])),\
        "out":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([100,n_classes]))}

bias={"bc1":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([depth_out1])),\
      "bc2":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([depth_out2])),\
      "bd1":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([512])),\
      "bd2":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([100])),\
      "out":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([n_classes]))}

##############卷积层和最大池化层定义

def conv2d(x,W,b,stride=1):
    x=tf.nn.conv2d(x,W,strides=[1,stride,stride,1],padding="SAME")
    x=tf.nn.bias_add(x,b)
    return tf.nn.relu(x)
def maxpool2d(x,stride=2):
    return tf.nn.max_pool(x,ksize=[1,stride,stride,1],strides=[1,stride,stride,1],padding="SAME")


####构建卷积神经网络+全连接层
def conv_net(x_,W,b):
    ####卷积层 1######
    conv1=conv2d(x_,W["wc1"],b["bc1"])
    conv1=maxpool2d(conv1,2)
    
    ####卷积层 2######
    conv2=conv2d(conv1,W["wc2"],b["bc2"])
    conv2=maxpool2d(conv2,2)
    ####卷积层与全连接层连接#####
    fc1=tf.reshape(conv2,[-1,W["wd1"].get_shape().as_list()[0]])
    
    ####全连接层1#####
    fc1=tf.matmul(fc1,W["wd1"])
    fc1=tf.add(fc1,b["bd1"])
    fc1=tf.nn.relu(fc1)
    
    ####全连接层2#####
    fc2=tf.matmul(fc1,W["wd2"])
    fc2=tf.add(fc2,b["bd2"])
    fc2=tf.nn.relu(fc2)
    
    ######输出层####
    out=tf.matmul(fc2,W["out"])
    out=tf.add(out,b["out"])
    
    return out

########定义loss、optimizer#####
pred=conv_net(x_,Weights,bias) #网络预测值
loss=tf.reduce_mean(tf.nn.softmax_cross_entropy_with_logits_v2(logits=pred,labels=y_)) #损失函数
train_step=tf.train.AdamOptimizer(0.01).minimize(loss) #优化器

####模型评价
correct_pred=tf.equal(tf.argmax(pred,1),tf.argmax(y_,1))
accuracy=tf.reduce_mean(tf.cast(correct_pred,tf.float32))

init=tf.global_variables_initializer()
####################################################
## 训练
####################################################
start_time = time.time()
with tf.Session() as sess:
    sess.run(init)
    s_t=time.time()
    for  i  in range(epochs):
        train_data_batch=gen_small_data(train_X_shuffle_,train_Y_shuffle,batch_size)
        test_data_batch=gen_small_data(test_X_shuffle_,test_Y_shuffle,batch_size)
        for j in range(batch_num):
            x,y=next(train_data_batch)
            p,q=next(test_data_batch)
            if (p.shape)[0]<batch_size:
                test_data_batch=gen_small_data(test_X_shuffle_,test_Y_shuffle,batch_size)
                p,q=next(test_data_batch)       
            sess.run(train_step,feed_dict={x_:x,y_:y})
            cost,acc=sess.run([loss,accuracy],feed_dict={x_:x,y_:y})
            cost_t,acc_t=sess.run([loss,accuracy],feed_dict={x_:p,y_:q})
            if epochs%1==0:
                print("Train Epoch:",'%04d'%(i+1),"cost=","{:.9f}".format(cost),"Training accuracy","{:.5f}".format(acc))
                print("Test Epoch:",'%04d'%(i+1),"cost=","{:.9f}".format(cost_t),"Test accuracy","{:.5f}".format(acc_t))
    
    saver = tf.train.Saver()
    saver.save(sess,'./intel_test_model_6')
    print("Model restored.")
    
    e_t=time.time()
    print("Optimization Completed,running time %.2f seconds"%(e_t-s_t))

import time
epochs=10 #网络训练次数
learning_rate=0.01 #学习率
batch_size=512 #训练块的大小(mini-batch SGD)
batch_num=int(train_X_shuffle.shape[0]/batch_size) #块的数目

filter_width=3 #滤波器的宽度
filter_height=3 #滤波器的高度
depth_in=3 #输入数据通道数
depth_out1=64 #隐含层1的通道数(特征数目)
depth_out2=128#隐含层2的通道数(特征数目)
f_height=64 #输入图像尺寸

######输入
n_classes=6 ##手写字体10个类
x_=tf.placeholder(tf.float32,[batch_size,64,64,3]) #输入数据为100*100的图像，batch_size表示每次的训练样本个数
y_=tf.placeholder(tf.float32,[batch_size,n_classes]) #输出数据为6个类别

######ops:Weights and bias
Weights={"wc1":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([filter_height,filter_width,depth_in,depth_out1])),\
        "wc2":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([filter_height,filter_width,depth_out1,depth_out2])),\
        "wd1":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([int((f_height*f_height/16)*depth_out2),64])),\
         "wd2":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([64,32])),\
        "out":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([32,n_classes]))}

bias={"bc1":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([depth_out1])),\
      "bc2":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([depth_out2])),\
      "bd1":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([64])),\
      "bd2":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([32])),\
      "out":tf.Variable(tf.random_normal([n_classes]))}

##############卷积层和最大池化层定义

def conv2d(x,W,b,stride=1):
    x=tf.nn.conv2d(x,W,strides=[1,stride,stride,1],padding="SAME")
    x=tf.nn.bias_add(x,b)
    return tf.nn.relu(x)
def maxpool2d(x,stride=2):
    return tf.nn.max_pool(x,ksize=[1,stride,stride,1],strides=[1,stride,stride,1],padding="SAME")


####构建卷积神经网络+全连接层
def conv_net(x_,W,b):
    ####卷积层 1######
    conv1=conv2d(x_,W["wc1"],b["bc1"])
    conv1=maxpool2d(conv1,2)
    
    ####卷积层 2######
    conv2=conv2d(conv1,W["wc2"],b["bc2"])
    conv2=maxpool2d(conv2,2)
    ####卷积层与全连接层连接#####
    fc1=tf.reshape(conv2,[-1,W["wd1"].get_shape().as_list()[0]])
    
    ####全连接层1#####
    fc1=tf.matmul(fc1,W["wd1"])
    fc1=tf.add(fc1,b["bd1"])
    fc1=tf.nn.relu(fc1)
    
    ####全连接层2#####
    fc2=tf.matmul(fc1,W["wd2"])
    fc2=tf.add(fc2,b["bd2"])
    fc2=tf.nn.relu(fc2)
    
    ######输出层####
    out=tf.matmul(fc2,W["out"])
    out=tf.add(out,b["out"])
    
    return out

########定义loss、optimizer#####
pred=conv_net(x_,Weights,bias) #网络预测值
loss=tf.reduce_mean(tf.nn.softmax_cross_entropy_with_logits_v2(logits=pred,labels=y_)) #损失函数
train_step=tf.train.AdamOptimizer(learning_rate).minimize(loss) #优化器

####模型评价
correct_pred=tf.equal(tf.argmax(pred,1),tf.argmax(y_,1))
accuracy=tf.reduce_mean(tf.cast(correct_pred,tf.float32))

init=tf.global_variables_initializer()
####################################################
## 训练
####################################################
start_time = time.time()
with tf.Session() as sess:
    sess.run(init)
    s_t=time.time()
    for  i  in range(epochs):
        train_data_batch=gen_small_data(train_X_shuffle_,train_Y_shuffle,batch_size)
        test_data_batch=gen_small_data(test_X_shuffle_,test_Y_shuffle,batch_size)
        for j in range(batch_num):
            x,y=next(train_data_batch)
            p,q=next(test_data_batch)
            if (p.shape)[0]<batch_size:
                test_data_batch=gen_small_data(test_X_shuffle_,test_Y_shuffle,batch_size)
                p,q=next(test_data_batch)       
            sess.run(train_step,feed_dict={x_:x,y_:y})
            cost,acc=sess.run([loss,accuracy],feed_dict={x_:x,y_:y})
            cost_t,acc_t=sess.run([loss,accuracy],feed_dict={x_:p,y_:q})
            if epochs%1==0:
                print("Train Epoch:",'%04d'%(i+1),"cost=","{:.9f}".format(cost),"Training accuracy","{:.5f}".format(acc))
                print("Test Epoch:",'%04d'%(i+1),"cost=","{:.9f}".format(cost_t),"Test accuracy","{:.5f}".format(acc_t))
    
    saver = tf.train.Saver()
    saver.save(sess,'./intel_test_model_6.ckpt')
    print("Model restored.")
    
    e_t=time.time()
    print("Optimization Completed,running time %.2f seconds"%(e_t-s_t))
